snippet: A House committee hearing showed little sign that the bipartisan effort to build a women’s history museum in Washington is gaining the momentum it needs.
abstract: House committee hearing shows little sign of momentum on bill that could ultimately lead to the construction of a women's history museum in Washington DC.
lead_paragraph: A House committee hearing showed little sign that the bipartisan effort to build a women’s history museum in Washington is gaining the momentum it needs.

headline.main: Slow Progress on Support for Women’s Museum
headline.print_headline: Slow Progress On Support For Museum On Women
